  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening pastoral processes in peace building, human rights and care for Our Common Home -IFI</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COVID has affected Colombia significantly and the pandemic, as well as the measures in response have exacerbated underlying issues, including having an impact the economic and socio-political stability. This project seeks to strengthen a coordinated response under the leadership of SNPS-Caritas Colombia, working together with four Church Provinces and Ecclesiastical Jurisdictions (EJ). Project participants will engage in research, training and advocacy-including communication- related to peace and reconciliation, protection of human rights and care for the common home.</narrative>
  </description>
